column5: Unfortunately I don't receive the channel. Next time, I'll have to go over to my Dad's.  Has has one of the zillion channel package deals. No pm ...  No problem.    Registered Letter on it's way

On the moderators board I have a list of everyone who entered with a # bedside their name.  I need someone to pick 3 numbers between 1 and 32 asap.   Theres free tickets to the spring fishing show in it for the forst person to post the #'s  Ill then go match the numbers AND I have an extra surprise as well!!  This way its totally at random!
Thanks Fish 4 eyes!!  Pm me your mailing address and Ill get the hat out to ya!!  Ill be right back!!

OK!!   The winners are:  #3 - Bucktail #13 - Joey (she's still got her horseshoe!!) and #25 - Skud   AND, here's the surprise, Dave appreciates everyone's time to post here so, just for posting EVERYONE who entered is gonna get a Facts of Fishing T-shirt  Thanks Dave for all your support.  So if ya won the main prizes and if ya want the shirt, PM me your full Name, mailing address AND shirt size!!
No WAYYY!!!! That is super cool  :D PM Sent!  And congrats to the lucky so and so's who won the tackle
